        "text": "Hi all - here are some of my music projects:\n\n*Minutes*\n<https:\/\/www.listenfaster.com\/main\/1min\/> is my daily sound journal, where I put up at least a minute of sound a day - a sketch, a demo, a field recording, something I heard that day, a thought and a picture.  Totally for my own reflection but I think anyone would benefit from this kind of practice, regardless of your creative outlet.",
