        "client_msg_id": "1cc6d901-3f39-4996-9593-d064e7f54506",
        "text": "*The Guitar Cult*\nA lot of pre-composed guitar ensemble stuff for a band of guitarists I put together. Focused on lots of interlocking things that are fun to play together.  <https:\/\/www.theguitarcult.com\/visual-evidence\/>\nI have a publisher who also taught an ensemble course during covid, and the students made videos for these pieces of mine they learned.  They're kinda slick. A very nice thing to happen to me during lockdown.\n\n<https:\/\/youtu.be\/hmvI6H64SPI>\n\n<https:\/\/youtu.be\/hmvI6H64SPI>\n\nOur first performance had 11 guitars with Ebows, and I tried to make some Xenakis\/Ligeti-like soundmasses with them.\n\n<https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/watch?v=-V9oJ5U5RzQ>",
